关税」名单，俄罗斯不在其中。一名白宫官员解释说，俄罗斯「不在这个名单上，因为与乌克兰战争相关的制裁已经使两国之间的贸易额为零」。 梅德韦杰夫还认为，美国征收关税的后果将是全球性的。梅德韦杰夫在 Telegram 上写道，「特朗普对几乎全世界（国家）征收关税，严重扭曲了全球贸易体系。其后果将是全球性的。」梅德韦杰夫回应俄不在美「对等关税」名单上，还用错了一句中国古话"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1768996550896b135bf9231aa44d330d_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1891284047193424538"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIt4ed/9PYrZJ8EAMaCTExNDMyMDk0MiDn6rq/BjAAOL4HQB1yEzE4OTEyODQwNDcxOTM0MjQ1Mzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1857515993426948096", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTg1NzUxNTk5MzQyNjk0ODA5NnITMTg1NzUxNTk5MzQyNjk0ODA5NngA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1857515993426948096", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTg1NzUxNTk5MzQyNjk0ODA5NnITMTg1NzUxNTk5MzQyNjk0ODA5NngA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}]}